# User Interface Design Document

## Design Philosophy
- Clean, editorial aesthetic with emphasis on typography and whitespace
- Content-first approach with minimal distractions
- Subtle depth through gradients and blur effects
- Balanced mix of serif and sans-serif typography

## Layout Structure
- Single-column layout optimized for readability
- Maximum content width of 42rem (672px)
- Wider header/footer containers (60rem)
- Fixed header with subtle blur effect
- Generous vertical spacing between sections

## Core Components

### Header
- Height: 4.5rem (72px)
- Background: white/90 with backdrop-blur-[6px]
- Subtle border: #E6E1D7/80
- Custom "jkYau" logotype with precise letter positioning
- Right-aligned navigation items

### Hero Section
- Subtle gradient background (from-[#E6E1D7]/80 to-[#E6E1D7]/40)
- Large serif heading (3.25rem)
- Two-tier description with opacity variation
- Social links with understated hover effects
- Rounded corners (rounded-2xl)
- Comfortable padding (p-12)

### Content Areas
- Clear section headings (1.5rem)
- Consistent vertical rhythm
- Generous whitespace between elements
- Group hover effects on interactive elements
- Subtle transitions for all interactions

### Footer
- Matches header styling
- Logo and copyright on left
- RSS link on right
- Consistent height with header

## Typography System

### Logo Treatment
- Font: Times New Roman
- Size: 1.5rem
- Custom letter spacing and positioning
- Precisely rotated 'a' (-rotate-12)
- Origin point: 25% 40%

### Content Typography
- **Headers:**
  - Hero: 3.25rem, serif
  - Section: 1.5rem, sans-serif
  - Post titles: 1.75rem, serif
  
- **Body Text:**
  - Primary: 1.125rem, serif
  - Meta: 15px, sans-serif
  - Links: 15px, sans-serif

## Color Palette
- **Backgrounds:**
  - Main: #FAF9F7 (warm white)
  - Header/Footer: white/90 with blur
  - Feature: #E6E1D7/80 to #E6E1D7/40 gradient
  
- **Text:**
  - Primary: #1A1919
  - Secondary: #666666
  - Hover states: Opacity variations

## Spacing System
- **Vertical:**
  - Page top: pt-24
  - Page bottom: pb-16
  - Section spacing: mb-20
  - Content gaps: space-y-10
  
- **Horizontal:**
  - Container: px-6
  - Element gaps: gap-5, gap-6, gap-8

## Interactive Elements
- **Links:**
  - Subtle underlines on hover
  - Color transitions (duration-200)
  - Consistent hover states
  
- **Groups:**
  - Smooth opacity changes
  - Text color transitions
  - No harsh state changes

## Responsive Design
- **Desktop:**
  - Fixed header
  - Optimal reading width
  - Full feature set
  
- **Mobile:**
  - Preserved typography scale
  - Adjusted padding
  - Maintained hierarchy
  - Stack layout preservation

## Performance
- Minimal CSS usage
- No heavy animations
- Efficient blur effects
- System fonts
- Optimized transitions

## Accessibility
- High contrast text
- Clear visual hierarchy
- Semantic HTML
- Proper heading structure
- Adequate text sizing
- Consistent navigation patterns
- Hover/focus states 